<%= stylesheet_link_tag "back-ab-princ-col-new", :media => "all"  %>   
<% @title = "About CGT Page Back - New About Our Principles Column" -%>
<% @header = "About CGT Page Back - New About Our Principles Column" -%>
<div id="operate-mgt">
  <div id="operate-intro">
    <h3>Information About Our Guiding Principles Column</h3>
    <p>The column is only text. The font size is 14px, and the color is pink. The size of the display box is 475x135px.
    <p>In the column, at most, there are 2 paragraphes in it. In one paragraph case, it includes about 560 letters(70 letters X 8 lines); In two paragraphes case, it has about 490 letters. If the input is longer than the limit, the rest will be cut. Please pay attention to it.
    <p>After you input the new content, then it will replace your old one that will be changed. </p>
  </div><!-- end #operate-intro -->

  <div id="operate-area">
    <h3>New About Our Guiding Principles Column</h3>
    
    <div id="operate-new">
        <% form_for :about,@about,:url => { :action => "create_princ",:id => @princ.id }, :html => { :method => :post } do |f| %>
          <div class="word">
            <p>New Comment:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 220 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="message">
            <%= f.text_area :content %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p>New Author:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <%= f.text_field :author %>
          </div>
          <div class="word">
            <p>New Admin:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Less than 40 letters.)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <input name="Admin" type="text" class="input" maxlength=40 size=50 />
          </div>
          <div class="div">
            <p>
              <%= f.submit "New Content" ,:popup => "New Content Has Been Successfully Input!" %>
            </p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>    <!-- End #operate-new -->

      <div id="operate-buttons">
        <ul>
          <li><%= link_to "Back" ,:action => "princ"%></li>
        </ul>
      </div>  <!-- End #operate-bottons -->

    </div>   <!-- end #operate-area -->
    
  </div>  <!-- end #operate-mgt -->